des: The Beatrice Rotary Club promotes service before self and volunteering in the Gage County area and around the world. Please try out our skill to stay informed about what's going on with our group and the latest information available. Ask Beatrice Rotary what are the upcoming events? What is going on this week? What is the rotary foundation? How do i get in contact?
